OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few brighter intervals are
OL,6,Fpossible this morning, but it will
OL,7,Fgradually cloud over, with patchy
OL,8,Flight rain developing this afternoon,
OL,9,Fturning more persistent by the end of
OL,10,Fthe day. Turning blustery but
OL,11,Fremaining mild for late February.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a cloudy evening
OL,14,Fand night with further outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain, this locally heavy at first, but
OL,16,Fturning light and patchy later.
OL,17,FAnother mild and frost free night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
