OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA cloudy and often damp
OL,6,Fmorning with outbreaks of light rain
OL,7,Fand drizzle.The occasional brighter
OL,8,Fbreak during the afternoon, though
OL,9,Ffurther heavy rain possible later.
OL,10,FMild and breezy at times.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FOvernight rain slowly giving way to
OL,14,Fdrier and brighter skies on Saturday.
OL,15,FTurning damp and windy on Sunday.
OL,16,FBrighter, but still showery and breezy
OL,17,Fon Monday. Briefly cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
